*"Stići će do cilja za par sati." (He will reach the destination in a few hours.)

*"Ona je stigla ranije nego što su očekivali." (She arrived earlier than they expected.)

*"On nikada nije stigao da ispuni svoj plan." (He never managed to fulfill his plan.)

*"Vreme je stiglo da promenimo stvari." (The time has come to change things.)

*"Stigla mu je vest da mu je otac bolestan." (He received the news that his father was ill.)